page.title: 12Living In Keynsham In 1985
page.content: { The next three pages were compiled by {Sasha Davies,Sacha Reeves,Hannah Baker The part of Keynsham where I live is quite new.The things I like doing with my family is going up to Keynsham High Street normally on a Saturday.There are lots of shops that sell all different things.I like looking in the shops that sell jewellery and pencils and things like that.Keynsham is quite crowded if you go up on a Saturday probably because it is the nearest place that has supermarkets.Sometimes me and my friends from school go up to Keynsham High Street and have a look around.Sometimes my family and I go swimming in the local swimming baths. Also I like looking in the pet shop because I have a rabbit called Sniff. He is quite big even though he is not one yet,we got him last August.My house is quite new but it is {cont.
